<PB REF="008042_0001_102E1C51088E4308">
<P>The CHRISTIAN SOLDIER'S DUTY; the Lawfulne&s;s and Dignity of his Office; and the Importance of the <HI>Prote&s;tant Cau&s;e</HI> in the Briti&s;h Colonies, &s;tated and explained.</P>
<P>A SERMON, Preached <HI>April</HI> 5, 1757. IN <HI>CHRIST-CHURCH, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="UOM" EXTENT="1 word"></HI> To the fir&s;t Battalion of his Maje&s;ty's ROYAL AMERICAN REGIMENT at the Reque&s;t of their COLONEL and OFFICERS.</P>
<P><HI>By</HI> WILLIAM SMITH <HI>A.M. <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="UOM" EXTENT="1 span"></HI> Philadelphia.</P>
<P>To which is annexed, A <HI>PRAYER</HI> on the &s;ame Occa&s;ion.</P>
<P><HI>PHILADELPHIA:</HI> Printed and Sold by JAMES CHATTIN. 1757 <HI>[Price One Shilling]</HI></P>
</DIV1>
