AND DEPUTY QUARTER-MASTER-GENERAL of all HIS MAJESTY'S Forces, rai&s;ed or to be rai&s;ed: As a &s;incere Te&s;timony of E&s;teem for His public Character, and Friend&s;hip for His Per&s;on, this SERMON, preached and pub|li&s;hed at His Reque&s;t, is</P>
